## 3.0

- Removed lots of cruft (#19)
- IncomingMessage has replace MailRequest as the default message class. If you
  still want to use MailRequest, decorate your handlers with the new filters (#21)
- Introduced filters to automatically convert incoming mail to a format you want
  (current we support both MailRequest and standard email objects) (#21)
- Moved from modargs to argparse - command line interface has changed (#28)
- Moved from PyDNS to dnspython
- Tests can now be run without having to start a log-server first (#6)
